toRomanNumerals_v3 14
toRomanNumerals_v3 19
toRomanNumerals_v3 1947
toRomanNumerals_v3 1999

// test it on all the numbers up to 30
[1..30] |> List.map toRomanNumerals_v3 |> String.concat ","

